properties.property: select A.Prcsname Process, b.descr Description,a.recurname, a.ENDDTTM Finished FROM SYSADM.PS_PMN_PRCSLIST A, SYSADM.PS_PRCSDEFN B WHERE A.OPRID = 'PRCSSCH' AND B.PRCSTYPE = A.PRCSTYPE AND B.PRCSNAME = A.PRCSNAME AND TO_DATE(TO_CHAR(A.RUNDTTM,'DD-MON-YYYY')) = TO_DATE(TO_CHAR(SYSDATE ,'DD-MON-YYYY')) AND A.RECURNAME in ('DWPERIODS','DWDAILY','DWENCSUM','DWNIGHTLY') order by a.recurname,a.PRCSNAME

DTS:Executable.DTS:refId: Package\Common for Tabular Models\SQL New Partition?
DTS:Executable.DTS:TaskContact: Execute SQL Task; Microsoft Corporation; SQL Server 2014; © 2014 Microsoft Corporation; All Rights Reserved;http://www.microsoft.com/sql/support/default.asp;1

SQLTask:SqlTaskData.SQLTask:SqlStatementSource:
Declare @PartitionNumber int
set @PartitionNumber = (select cast(max(value)as int) as PartitionNumber from sys.partition_range_values prv
inner join sys.partition_functions pf
on prv.function_id=pf.function_id
where pf.name='FiscalYearPF')
ALTER PARTITION SCHEME FiscalYearPS NEXT USED [PRIMARY]
if (year(Getdate()) + 3 > @PartitionNumber) ALTER PARTITION FUNCTION FiscalYearPF() SPLIT RANGE (@PartitionNumber+1);
